snippet.title: Profanity Police Trailer (In Game)
snippet.description:
Profanity Police is the first game by The Ugly Cygnet.

This is a sample of gameplay created as a trailer for steam available mid 2024.

This video does not contain explicit language but the game contains language not suitable for children.
